strings.Value: "What a beautiful sky. I remember a similar sky in Hajoth Hakados, when Octavia and I hid on a roof, escaping from the Technic League's agents."
"What is this I hear – Regongar talking about beauty? I was hoping at least this one vice was alien to you! Well, now I guess you embody absolutely everything I hate!"
"It's surprising to hear you speak of the beauty of the sky. You seem more like someone who kicks people for admiring the sky, not doing it yourself."

"You know what surprises me most about your stories? How — how did the Technic League let you escape so many times? If the resources and people they assigned to catching slaves were instead focused on guarding them in the first place, their problems would be solved..."
